[Konsep Perbandingan -- Campuran] \textbf{
Perbandingan A : B $= 2 : 3$, sehingga dari $5$ bagian total:
\[
\text{Harga campuran} = \frac{2 \times 12.000 + 3 \times 18.000}{2 + 3}
= \frac{24.000 + 54.000}{5}
= \frac{78.000}{5}
= Rp15.600
\]

[Geometri Dasar -- Lingkaran Dalam] \textbf{
Sisi miring: $c = \sqrt{6^2 + 8^2} = \sqrt{100} = 10$ cm.
Rumus jari-jari lingkaran dalam segitiga siku-siku:
\[
r = \frac{a + b - c}{2} = \frac{6 + 8 - 10}{2} = \frac{4}{2} = \mathbf{2\ \text{cm}}
\]

[Persamaan Kuadrat -- Hubungan Akar] \textbf{
Dari persamaan $x^2 + px + q = 0$: $\alpha + \beta = -p$ dan $\alpha\beta = q$.
\[
\alpha^2\beta + \alpha\beta^2 = \alpha\beta (\alpha + \beta) = q \cdot (-p) = \mathbf{-pq}
\]

[Trigonometri -- Rumus Jumlah ke Perkalian] \textbf{
Gunakan rumus $\sin A - \sin B = 2\cos\!\dfrac{A+B}{2}\sin\!\dfrac{A-B}{2}$:
\[
\sin 75^\circ - \sin 15^\circ
= 2\cos 45^\circ \sin 30^\circ
= 2 \cdot \frac{\sqrt{2}}{2} \cdot \frac{1}{2}
= \frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}
\]

[Fungsi Invers] \textbf{
Misalkan $y = \dfrac{2x+1}{x-1}$, cari $x$ dalam bentuk $y$:
\[
y(x-1) = 2x + 1 \implies xy - y = 2x + 1 \implies x(y-2) = y + 1 \implies x = \frac{y+1}{y-2}
\]
\[
f^{-1}(x) = \frac{x+1}{x-2} \implies f^{-1}(3) = \frac{3+1}{3-2} = \frac{4}{1} = \mathbf{4}
\]

[Kalkulus -- Turunan Aturan Hasil Bagi] \textbf{
Gunakan $\left(\dfrac{u}{v}\right)' = \dfrac{u'v - uv'}{v^2}$ dengan $u = x^2+3x,\ v = x+1$:
\[
f'(x) = \frac{(2x+3)(x+1) - (x^2+3x)(1)}{(x+1)^2}
= \frac{2x^2+5x+3 - x^2-3x}{(x+1)^2}
= \frac{x^2+2x+3}{(x+1)^2}
\]
\[
f'(2) = \frac{4 + 4 + 3}{(3)^2} = \frac{11}{9}
\]
